### Backend API Test Suite
### Base URL: http://localhost:3001

### ============================================
### 1. Health Check
### ============================================

### Check backend health
GET http://localhost:3001/api/health

###

### ============================================
### 2. Agent Management
### ============================================

### List all available agents
GET http://localhost:3001/api/agents

###

### ============================================
### 3. File Processing - CSV Analyst Agent
### ============================================

### Submit CSV for processing (CSV Analyst)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/process
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.csv"
Content-Type: text/csv

name,email,department,salary
Alice Johnson,alice@company.com,Engineering,120000
Bob Smith,bob@company.com,Sales,90000
Charlie Brown,charlie@company.com,Engineering,125000
Diana Prince,diana@company.com,HR,85000
Edward Norton,edward@company.com,Sales,95000
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="agentId"

csv-analyst
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

###

### ============================================
### 3b. File Processing - Data Quality Auditor
### ============================================

### Submit CSV for processing (Data Quality Auditor)
# @name startProcess
POST http://localhost:3001/api/process
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sales-data.csv"
Content-Type: text/csv

product,quantity,price,date
Widget A,100,29.99,2024-01-01
Widget B,50,,2024-01-02
Widget C,75,19.99,2024-01-03
Widget A,100,29.99,2024-01-04
Widget D,25,49.99,
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="agentId"

data-quality-auditor
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

###

### ============================================
### 4. Session Management
### ============================================

### Get session status (replace {SESSION_ID} with actual ID from POST response)
# @name getSessionStatus
GET http://localhost:3001/api/process/{{startProcess.response.body.sessionId}}

###

### List output files for a session
# @name listOutputFiles
GET http://localhost:3001/api/process/{{startProcess.response.body.sessionId}}/files

###

### Download a generated file (replace {FILE_ID} with actual ID)
# @name downloadFile
GET http://localhost:3001/api/process/{{startProcess.response.body.sessionId}}/files/{{listOutputFiles.response.body.files[0].fileId}}/download

###

### ============================================
### 5. Error Cases
### ============================================

### Missing required file
POST http://localhost:3001/api/process
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="agentId"

csv-analyst
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

###

### Wrong file type (not CSV)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/process
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="data.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

This is not a CSV file
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="agentId"

csv-analyst
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

###

### Invalid agent ID
POST http://localhost:3001/api/process
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.csv"
Content-Type: text/csv

name,email
Alice,alice@company.com
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="agentId"

nonexistent-agent
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

###

### Nonexistent session
GET http://localhost:3001/api/process/invalid-session-id

###

### ============================================
### USAGE INSTRUCTIONS
### ============================================
###
### To use this file with VS Code:
### 1. Install "REST Client" extension (humao.rest-client)
### 2. Open this file (requests.http)
### 3. Click "Send Request" above any request to execute it
###
### Tips:
### - Copy SESSION_ID from POST /api/process response to test GET requests
### - Copy FILE_ID from GET /api/process/{SESSION_ID}/files response
### - Use the mock agent (default) or set USE_COPILOT_SDK=true for real SDK
### - SSE streaming is not directly testable here; use browser DevTools or curl
###
### Example workflow:
### 1. POST /api/process to create a session and get {SESSION_ID}
### 2. Replace {SESSION_ID} in GET requests
### 3. GET /api/process/{SESSION_ID} to check status
### 4. GET /api/process/{SESSION_ID}/files to list outputs
### 5. GET /api/process/{SESSION_ID}/files/{FILE_ID}/download to retrieve file
###
